    <div class="guide-content wow-panel">
        <div class="panel-header">Why Fire?</div>
        <div class="panel-content">
            <p>Fire Mages are one of the strongest DPS specs throughout TBC Classic, scaling incredibly well with gear as the expansion progresses. The 2/48/11 build maximizes Fire damage through Ignite, Fire Power, and Empowered Fireball while dipping into Frost for the powerful Icy Veins haste cooldown. Your rotation revolves around Fireball spam with Scorch weaving to maintain the Fire Vulnerability debuff.</p>

            <h3>Key Talents</h3>
            <div class="talent-explanations">
                <div class="talent-explain">
                    <img src="https://wow.zamimg.com/images/wow/icons/medium/spell_fire_incinerate.jpg" alt="Ignite" class="explain-icon">
                    <div>
                        <h4>Ignite</h4>
                        <p>Your Fire crits cause the target to burn for an additional 40% of your spell's damage over 4 seconds. Stacks and rolls with multiple crits for massive damage.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="talent-explain">
                    <img src="https://wow.zamimg.com/images/wow/icons/medium/spell_fire_sealoffire.jpg" alt="Combustion" class="explain-icon">
                    <div>
                        <h4>Combustion</h4>
                        <p>Each Fire spell hit increases your crit chance by 10% until you land 3 crits. Amazing burst cooldown that synergizes with Ignite.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="talent-explain">
                    <img src="https://wow.zamimg.com/images/wow/icons/medium/spell_fire_flamebolt.jpg" alt="Empowered Fireball" class="explain-icon">
                    <div>
                        <h4>Empowered Fireball</h4>
                        <p>Your Fireball gains an additional 15% of your bonus spell damage. Massive scaling talent that makes Fire better with every gear upgrade.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="talent-explain">
                    <img src="https://wow.zamimg.com/images/wow/icons/medium/spell_frost_coldhearted.jpg" alt="Icy Veins" class="explain-icon">
                    <div>
                        <h4>Icy Veins</h4>
                        <p>20% spell haste for 20 seconds with pushback immunity. The reason you invest 11 points into Frost — a massive DPS cooldown.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <h3>Stat Priority</h3>
            <ol>
                <li><strong>Hit Rating</strong> (until 16% cap / 202 rating)</li>
                <li><strong>Spell Damage</strong></li>
                <li><strong>Spell Haste</strong></li>
                <li><strong>Spell Critical Strike</strong></li>
